name: Praise your titans
description: 'Make them live' - This image is also an object; a projection and a materialization, a physical being inside a digital one. Through steganography, I've placed a .glb file with the 3D model inside the image. The buyer will get the password that will allow the .glb to be extracted and used as a prop on some metaverse (or 3D printed and worshipped at an altar).
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
